{"tid":1765801,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「以正視聽」 港島大遊行係必定會失敗","createTime":"2019-12-02T06:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T12:13:10.000Z","uid":22717,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a88b2eaa7968c16a7b3f2347d9d47d4874a4de16","tid":1765801,"uid":22717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T06:33:26.000Z","msg":"Formula:<br />\n1.連登又吹風大遊行 <br />\n理由不外乎：俾外國睇到民意，穩定軍心<br />\n2.民陣又真係會申請不反，好多人又會推百萬遊行<br />\n3.99%失敗上訴後再失敗 1%下面再講<br />\n4.當日一早周圍重防，真係入到去既人得返好少<br />\n5.大圍捕。<br />\n<br />\n唔單止做唔到大家想要既效果 更會損失大量手足，再focus左落警暴到<br />\n最好既例子就係929<br />\n有人話有不反就得 但你睇下112既plan b? 劇情一模一樣<br />\n你估12月9仲會俾你好似琴日12月1咁和平？ <br />\n尖沙咀都易走啲 但港島就一定要過海 封哂三隧點走<br />\n<br />\n星期六日既大遊行除左對個個地方例如油尖旺，港島有影響就冇其他影響<br />\n<br />\n利申香城online玩家"},{"pid":"d8b4364cd4c9cba7be70db41c499dff36f069c2d","tid":1765801,"uid":22717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T06:33:36.000Z","msg":"612"},{"pid":"3fd623d1ad3d8af9803f16204a4e9cf7d16ddbcc","tid":1765801,"uid":82068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T08:28:56.000Z","msg":"一早講左狗改不了吃屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BM5APxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBM5APxB.jpg&h=0d53d37f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a5e520c0261ca99220528e4372918439a99c0aa","tid":1765801,"uid":22717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:30:32.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"3987c17cc004b0fec00a6059ce6734e5627eab4c","tid":1765801,"uid":22717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"101"},{"pid":"b27e7b64f5eb430225be46680fc0329ff9df38a3","tid":1765801,"uid":22717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:31:16.000Z","msg":"1111"},{"pid":"5881ca99efd0b5f09ea9b764bee2ca81790be05b","tid":1765801,"uid":213978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201